      <div class="block block-block first last odd" id="block-block-11">
       <h2>
        Giving all members of the Harvard community a stake in the campus we share
       </h2>
       <p>
        The Harvard Solution Space is a forum for open discussion that is designed to engage our community’s collective wisdom. The Solution Space is now closed, but you can browse the solutions that have been submitted below.
        <a href="https://inclusionandbelongingtaskforce.harvard.edu/" target="_blank">
         View the final report of the Presidential Task Force on Inclusion and Belonging.
        </a>
       </p>
       <p>
       </p>
      </div>
     </div>
